        "uuid": "daed99e3_1b8d9e6f",
        "filename": "experimental/multi-skp/SkMultiSkp.h",
        "patchSetId": 3
      },
      "lineNbr": 12,
      "author": {
        "id": 5045
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-05-07T13:34:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We tend to use SkSemaphore for this sort of thing where you\u0027d use a condition variable.  See e.g. the implementation of SkThreadPool.\n\nI\u0027m coming in late at this.  Are we all confident that this code reflects a plan we like?",
      "parentUuid": "487cddf1_ddcfe785",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 12,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 12,
        "endChar": 29
      },
      "revId": "ad461f1b2ebc939b6afef7b31408b007cae78ffb",
